incident_updates.body: This incident has been resolved.
We have resolved the issue regarding service degradation with Zoom meetings. We will continue to monitor and provide updates as we have them.
We have identified the issue and are working on remediation. We will continue to provide updates as we have them.

Our monitoring has detected service degradation in India where the Zoom meeting service mentioned below are impacted. Our engineers are currently investigating the impact and root cause. Zoom will provide updates as soon as there is more information to share.

incidents.name: Issue joining Zoom meetings in Brazil

incident_updates.body: Between 2:34 pm - 2:59 pm UTC our monitoring detected service degradation in Brazil affecting Zoom Meeting. During this time some customer may have experienced issues joining Zoom Meetings.

incidents.name: Issue with Zoom Phone in China

incident_updates.body: Between 18:53 - 19:14 UTC our monitoring detected service degradation in China affecting Zoom Phone.  During this time some customers may not have been able to use the Zoom Phone service.
